OL,3,CFirst drug consumption room should not
OL,4,Cbe seen as 'silver bullet', says MP
OL,6,FThe UK's first safer drugs consumption
OL,7,Froom should not be seen as a "silver
OL,8,Fbullet" to tackle Scotland's drug
OL,9,Fdeaths, the chairwoman of a
OL,10,FWestminster committee has said.
OL,12,FMPs on the Scottish Affairs Committee
OL,13,Fsaid funding for The Thistle in
OL,14,FGlasgow should not come at the expense
OL,15,Fof other efforts to reduce drug harm.
