OL,3,CFirst drug consumption room should not
OL,4,Cbe seen as 'silver bullet', says MP
OL,6,FIn a report published on Tuesday, they
OL,7,Fsaid the UK Government should not make
OL,8,Fup its mind on the future of the
OL,9,FThistle before an expert evaluation
OL,10,Ftakes place on the three-year pilot
OL,11,Fscheme.
OL,13,FThe Thistle which officially opened in
OL,14,FJanuary, is a space where drug users
OL,15,Fcan take illegal substances such as
OL,16,Fheroin and cocaine under medical
OL,17,Fsupervision in a hygienic environment.
