OL,3,CFirst drug consumption room should not
OL,4,Cbe seen as 'silver bullet', says MP
OL,6,FIt is designed to reduce public drug
OL,7,Fuse and help tackle Scotland's drug
OL,8,Fdeaths rate, which is the worst in
OL,9,FEurope.
OL,11,FHowever the committee's report notes
OL,12,Fthat it is not anticipated to have an
OL,13,Fimpact on the national or city-wide
OL,14,Fdrug death rates, though it is
OL,15,F"likely" to reduce them locally.
OL,17,FThe report said concerns from nearby
OL,18,Fresidents must be "taken seriously"
OL,19,Fand a "responsive communication
OL,20,Fstrategy" must be put in place as soon
OL,21,Fas possible.
