OL,3,CFirst drug consumption room should not
OL,4,Cbe seen as 'silver bullet', says MP
OL,6,FIt also said the introduction of a
OL,7,Froom for inhaling drugs, as opposed to
OL,8,Finjecting them, should be considered
OL,9,Ffor The Thistle.
OL,11,FThe MPs noted the Thistle is
OL,12,F"expensive" and any future facilities
OL,13,Fcould be less sophisticated in order
OL,14,Fto save money.
OL,16,FPatricia Ferguson, chairwoman of the
OL,17,FScottish Affairs Committee, said:
OL,18,F"Scotland has the highest rate of drug-
OL,19,Frelated deaths in Europe.
