OL,3,CFirst drug consumption room should not
OL,4,Cbe seen as 'silver bullet', says MP
OL,6,F"Without a doubt, this is the most
OL,7,Fpressing public health issue facing
OL,8,Fthe nation and things need to change
OL,9,Furgently to stop more people dying.
OL,11,F"The Thistle could be one way of
OL,12,Fhelping Scotland do this.
OL,14,F"If the facility, after its three-year
OL,15,Fpilot, is shown to be effective at
OL,16,Ftackling drug-related harm, we're
OL,17,Furging the UK Government to follow the
OL,18,Fevidence, and take the legislative
OL,19,Faction needed to create a proper legal
OL,20,Fframework that will ensure it can run
OL,21,Fand be regulated properly."
