OL,3,CFirst drug consumption room should not
OL,4,Cbe seen as 'silver bullet', says MP
OL,6,FShe continued: "However, we also
OL,7,Frecognise that The Thistle is not a
OL,8,Fsilver bullet.
OL,10,F"Our report emphasises that this pilot
OL,11,Fshouldn't come at the cost of other
OL,12,Frecovery services ` rather, they
OL,13,Fshould operate in tandem to offer as
OL,14,Fmuch help as possible to people with
OL,15,Fproblem drug use."
OL,17,FThe report also urged the Home Office
OL,18,Fto urgently complete its assessment of
OL,19,FThe Thistle for a drug checking
OL,20,Flicence ` which would allow visitors
OL,21,Fto have drugs chemically analysed.
