OL,3,CFirst drug consumption room should not
OL,4,Cbe seen as 'silver bullet', says MP
OL,6,FHolyrood drugs policy minister Maree
OL,7,FTodd said: "Drug deaths in Scotland
OL,8,Fare down 13% and at the lowest level
OL,9,Fsince 2017. The Scottish Government's
OL,10,Fnational mission to tackle drug harms
OL,11,Fmeans we have already spearheaded
OL,12,Fevidence-based harm reduction.
OL,14,F"Since opening, the Thistle has been
OL,15,Frecognised by the Global Commission on
OL,16,FDrug Policy and has responded to a
OL,17,Fnumber of on-site overdose incidents `
OL,18,FI have no doubt that lives have been
OL,19,Fsaved.
