OL,3,CFirst drug consumption room should not
OL,4,Cbe seen as 'silver bullet', says MP
OL,6,F"Evidence from similar facilities
OL,7,Faround the world has found that safer
OL,8,Fdrug consumption rooms can reduce
OL,9,Fharms, levels of public drug
OL,10,Fconsumption and publicly-discarded
OL,11,Fdrug-related litter.
OL,13,F"The UK overall is a clear outlier in
OL,14,FEurope for drugs deaths and in
OL,15,FScotland we are already working hard
OL,16,Ftogether with organisations to tackle
OL,17,Fthe challenge head-on, for example
OL,18,Fthrough creating more residential
OL,19,Frehabilitation beds and widening
OL,20,Faccess to naloxone.
